<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 01:00:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着机器人出租车的步伐加快，中国的司机和乘客都感到焦虑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-drivers-fret-robotaxis-pick-up-pace-passengers-2024-08-08/</link><description>刘毅是中国700万网约车司机之一。一名 36 岁的武汉居民今年开始兼职开车，当时全国范围内未售出公寓供过于求，建筑工程放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 00:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-drivers-fret-robotaxis-pick-up-pace-passengers-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：国防部长称韩国核武器将破坏美国关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korean-nuclear-weapons-would-fracture-us-ties-defence-chief-says-2024-08-07/</link><description>韩国国防部长申元植（Shin Won-sik）对路透社表示，如果韩国开始制造核武器，韩国可能会破坏与美国的联盟，并冲击金融市场，他驳回了国内再次呼吁韩国拥有自己的核武库来威慑朝鲜的呼声。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korean-nuclear-weapons-would-fracture-us-ties-defence-chief-says-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行的信心消退，防御仍坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 21:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>举重——中国选手侯勇蝉联女子49公斤级冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-hou-retains-womens-49kg-title-2024-08-07/</link><description>中国选手侯智慧在周三的巴黎奥运会举重比赛中以206公斤的总成绩卫冕49公斤级奥运会举重冠军，最终战胜罗马尼亚选手米哈埃拉·坎贝。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 20:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-hou-retains-womens-49kg-title-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>花样游泳——中国队大比分领先美国队夺得杂技团体赛首金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/artistic-swimming-china-win-gold-team-event-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三，中国队在巴黎奥运会花样游泳项目上凭借生动活泼的杂技表演赢得了评委们的赞叹，并以总成绩遥遥领先美国队夺得银牌，夺得了首枚金牌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/artistic-swimming-china-win-gold-team-event-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔兹与中国的悠久历史引来攻击和赞扬</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/walzs-long-history-with-china-draws-attacks-praise-2024-08-07/</link><description>副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选搭档、明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹正在引起美国共和党人和中国内部人士的关注，因为他与一个被视为华盛顿最大的经济和军事竞争对手的国家有着悠久的历史。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:41:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/walzs-long-history-with-china-draws-attacks-praise-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>举重——中国名将李娜卫冕61公斤级金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-li-fabin-wins-mens-61kg-gold-2024-08-07/</link><description>中国选手李发斌在周三的巴黎奥运会上以310公斤的总举重成绩卫冕61公斤级奥运会举重冠军，距离打破自己保持的世界纪录仅一步之遥。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-li-fabin-wins-mens-61kg-gold-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>巴西面临的中国家禽出口限制减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-facing-fewer-chinese-restrictions-poultry-exports-2024-08-07/</link><description>中国食品土畜进出口商会周三表示，自8月2日起对巴西家禽销售的限制仅适用于南里奥格兰德州的产品，该州上个月爆发了新城疫疫情。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:40:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-facing-fewer-chinese-restrictions-poultry-exports-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球-瑞典逆转击败日本夺得奖牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-men-beat-korea-swiftie-kaufmann-sends-germanys-women-into-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三，在巴黎奥运会男子乒乓球团体半决赛中，瑞典队在两场落后的情况下奋起反击，击败四号种子日本队，获得奖牌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:48:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-men-beat-korea-swiftie-kaufmann-sends-germanys-women-into-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>西门子能源首席执行官呼吁亚洲风电公司进入欧洲进行公平竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</link><description>西门子能源首席执行官周三表示，活跃在欧洲的中国和西方风力涡轮机制造商必须在相同的市场条件下销售产品，以创造公平竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>投资者在中国针对恒大集团提出清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三提交的一份股票文件显示，一名投资者已向中国法院提交请愿书，要求清算负债累累的房地产开发商中国恒大的一个主要部门。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>彪马因货运成本高、中国市场低迷而缩小了财年利润前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-narrows-fy-core-profit-outlook-2024-08-07/</link><description>德国运动服装制造商彪马周三缩小了全年核心利润预期，导致其股价短暂跌至 2018 年低点，理由是货运成本上升、汇率不利以及中国消费者信心持续低迷。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:14:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-narrows-fy-core-profit-outlook-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国在南海黄岩岛附近举行联合作战巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>南部战区在微信应用程序上发帖称，中国军队周三在南海黄岩岛附近组织海空联合作战巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡星展银行上调 2024 年预期，因强劲的财富流动推动利润增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</link><description>新加坡最大的银行星展集团受益于蓬勃发展的财富业务，将资产和费用收入推至创纪录水平，周三，星展集团上调了全年利润指引。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国进口恢复增长但出口放缓引发前景担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</link><description>7月份，中国的出口增长速度为三个月来最慢，低于预期，加剧了人们对庞大制造业前景的担忧，而在美国预期的科技限制措施之前急于增加芯片供应，导致进口增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:52:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>